description._content: Description: Police Station, La Digue. Built 1902. Location: La Digue, Seychelles Date: 1902 Description: View of Praslin from La Digue. Administrator about to embark on galley for "Alexandre." Location: La Digue, Seychelles Date: 1900-1929 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/771 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown. We have attempted to provide place information for the images automatically but our software may not have found the correct location.
